▷ GrammarTest
  ⧀ ⧂ CryptoPack
  ⧂ ⧃ CryptoPack
    ⏦ encrypt_fn
      ⏨ □ ⏨ Ⲷ
      ⏩
        □ ⬠ → H
        H ⬤ → MAC
        MAC ⬥ → CT
        CT ⇝
      ⏧
    ⏦ decrypt_fn
      ⏨ CT ⏨ MAC ⏨ Ⲷ
      ⏩
        CT ⬩ → PT
        PT ⬠ → H2
        H2 ≡ MAC
        H2 ≡ ◎
        PT ⇝
      ⏧
    ⧄ ⧂

  ⦜ StateInit
    ⦠ ⬠ → H0
    ⦝ StateInit → StateEncrypt
    ⦞ H0 ≡ ◎
  ⦜ StateEncrypt
    ⦠ H0 ⬥ → CT
    ⦝ StateEncrypt → StateVerify
    ⦞ CT ⪳ Ⲷ
  ⦜ StateVerify
    ⦠ CT ⬧ → ◎
    ⦝ StateVerify → StateFinal
  ⦣ StateFinal
    ⊙̂ ◎

  ⦂ □ ⪳ ⲻ
    ⦙ □ ⪳ Ⲹ
      ⥂ □
        ⥅ □ → item
        item ⬠ → itemH
        itemH ⊕ Σ → Σ
        ⥆
      ⥇
  ⦂ □ ⪳ ⲹ
    ⦙ ⦩ ⛯

  ⦦
    □ ⬨ → CT2
    ⦂ CT2 ≡ ✕
      ⦙ ⦪ CT2
    ⦨
      ⊙̂ ◎
  ⦧ ⦯ ⛯

  ⦰ □
    ⦱ ⦸
      □ → val
      val ⇝
    ⦱ ⦹
      ⭚ ⛯
    ⦱ ⦺
      val → result
      result ⇝
    ⦱ ⦻
      ⦩ ⛯

  ⣢
    ⣚ ⬠ → h1
    ⣚ ⬠ → h2
    ⣡ h1 h2
    h1 ⊕ h2 → combined
    combined ≡ ◎

  ⭐ → T0
  ⭒ ⭗ → elapsed
  ⦂ elapsed ⪱ ⭔
    ⦙ ⦩ ⛯

  ⬠ → finalHash
  finalHash ≡ ◎
  ◈ finalHash
  ⊙̂ ◎
◀
